ModificationUserName Property

CDXML Name:ModificationUserName
CDX Constant Name:kCDXProp_ModificationUserName
CDX Constant Value:0x0004
Data Size:CDXString
Property of objects:kCDXObj_Document
First written/read in:(not written/read)
Required?No

Description:

The name of the last modifier (program user's name) of the document.

If this property is absent:

This property is not read (or written) by ChemDraw, but is defined for future compatibility. There is no consequence to omitting it.
